    <div class="ask"><b>Put up a workshop</b><i>“Workshop June 12 in Seattle, $250 deposit.”</i><a data-ask="Put up a workshop" data-body="Mr Rogers — new workshop. Date/place/deposit: ">Ask now →</a></div>
