    <div class="want"><span class="em">🎙️</span><div>Your <b>real podcast episodes &amp; true numbers</b> — the current ones are placeholders on a trust-first brand.</div><a data-ask="My real episodes and numbers" data-body="Mr Rogers — here are my real episodes (titles + links) and the true stats: ">Send them →</a></div>
    <div class="want"><span class="em">🧾</span><div>Approve (or tweak) the <b>refund &amp; cancellation policy draft</b> — you sell $5,000 links with no stated terms.</div><a href="https://github.com/Braveplumhealing/graff-total-project/blob/main/docs/DRAFT-refund-policy.md">Read draft →</a></div>
    <div class="want"><span class="em">💌</span><div>Pick a <b>newsletter provider</b> (Buttondown or ConvertKit, free tiers) — the site already promises one.</div><a data-ask="Newsletter decision" data-body="Mr Rogers — let's set up the newsletter. I choose: ">Decide →</a></div>
    <div class="want"><span class="em">📊</span><div>Say yes to <b>privacy-friendly analytics</b> (Plausible/GoatCounter account, one script tag from us).</div><a data-ask="Analytics decision" data-body="Mr Rogers — yes to analytics. Provider I signed up for: ">Decide →</a></div>
    <div class="want"><span class="em">💬</span><div>Share 1–3 <b>real testimonials</b> (with permission) — the site's one quote is anonymous.</div><a data-ask="Testimonials" data-body="Mr Rogers — testimonials I have permission to share: ">Send them →</a></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section aria-label="How to reach Mr Rogers">
